title: It's Already Set Up | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: It's Already Set Up | Joel Osteen
description:
When God laid out the plan for your life, He lined up everything you need to fulfill your destiny. If you’ll stay in faith, you’re going to come in to what God has already set up. 



Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
